</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[178,1266,3158,3187]" pageId="15" pageNumber="64" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="15.[178,1384,2804,3460]" box="[178,1266,3158,3187]" pageId="15" pageNumber="64">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[178,412,3158,3187]" pageId="15" pageNumber="64">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Masoala Fork-marked 
<taxonomicName box="[802,896,3158,3187]" class="Mammalia" family="Lemuridae" genus="Lemur" kingdom="Animalia" order="Primates" pageId="15" pageNumber="64" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Lemur</taxonomicName>
is nocturnal and arboreal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
